Hardware Platform
-----------------

FPGA Address map:
                                     address
                                start       size
Microblaze local memory      0x00000000  0x00002000   (no TLM model)
External 1 MiB SRAM          0x20100000  0x00100000
GPIO 3x Push Buttons         0x40000000  0x00010000
GPIO 8x Leds                 0x40020000  0x00010000   (no TLM model)
GPIO 4x 7 Segment Display    0x40040000  0x00010000   (no TLM model)
GPIO 8x Dip Switches         0x40060000  0x00010000   (no TLM model)
UART Lite                    0x40600000  0x00010000   (no TLM model)
Interrupt Controller         0x41200000  0x00010000
Timer                        0x41C00000  0x00010000
VGA Controller               0x73A00000  0x00010000
